               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām "Miracles of Mary" (fols. 6ra-106va)
 I-1) Maṣḥafa
                     śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah and hymns (fols. 6ra-10rb)
 I-2)
                     Introductory exhortation (fols. 10rb-11vb)
 I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki
                     wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki... "I worship Thee..." (fols. 11vb-12vb)
 I-4) Taʾammǝra
                     Māryām "Miracles of Mary": 103 miracles (fols. 12va-106va)
 I-5) ʾAkkonu
                     bǝʾsi ... "Does not the man ..." (distributed among the miracles of Mary, fols.
                     25vb-46vb)
 
 Colophon.</summary>
